<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,151,501]" pageId="3" pageNumber="223">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,439,464]" pageId="3" pageNumber="223">Remarks.</emphasis>
We provide here, the second record of 
<taxonomicName box="[764,931,439,464]" class="Demospongiae" family="Metaniidae" genus="Drulia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Haplosclerida" pageId="3" pageNumber="223" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="cristata">
